    "The topic model captures the important intra-word/document statistical structure via a mixing distribution.",
    "LDA assumes words in each document are related and thus, topic assignment strongly relies on local co-occurrence.",
    "The documents are probability distributions over latent topics.",
    "While topics are probability distributions over words.",
    "For the evaluation of the LDA model, this study employed coherence score, perplexity, and human interpretation."
